description: Table showing how many people have claimed jobseeker's allowance (JSA) in each quarter since 1997; and what proportion in each quarter had been claiming JSA for (a) between 0 and 13 weeks, (b) between 13 and 26 weeks, (c) between 26 and 39 weeks, (d) between 39 and 52 weeks, (e) over 52 weeks and (f) over 104 weeks. 3 p.
